e</span> <span begin="00:03.081" end="00:03.373">verge</span> <span begin="00:03.373" end="00:03.492">of</span> <span begin="00:03.492" end="00:03.848">war</span> <span begin="00:03.848" end="00:04.035">with</span> <span begin="00:04.035" end="00:04.456">England</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">法国正处于与英国开战的边缘</span></p><p begin="00:04.862" end="00:07.679" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L3"><span begin="00:04.862" end="00:05.027">Now,</span> <span begin="00:05.027" end="00:05.207">do</span> <span begin="00:05.207" end="00:05.427">we</span> <span begin="00:05.427" end="00:05.814">provide</span> <span begin="00:05.814" end="00:06.123">aid</span> <span begin="00:06.123" end="00:06.224">and</span> <span begin="00:06.224" end="00:06.613">troops</span> <span begin="00:06.613" end="00:06.771">to</span> <span begin="00:06.771" end="00:06.891">our</span> <span begin="00:06.891" end="00:07.237">French</span> <span begin="00:07.237" end="00:07.679">allies</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">那么，我们是否要向法国盟友提供援助和兵力</span></p><p begin="00:07.689" end="00:09.140" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:07.689" end="00:07.825">Or</span> <span begin="00:07.825" end="00:08.009">do</span> <span begin="00:08.009" end="00:08.141">we</span> <span begin="00:08.141" end="00:08.534">stay</span> <span begin="00:08.534" end="00:08.754">out</span> <span begin="00:08.754" end="00:08.897">of</span> <span begin="00:08.897" end="00:09.140">it?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">还是说我们置身事外？</span></p><p begin="00:09.427" end="00:11.402" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:09.427" end="00:09.939">Remember,</span> <span begin="00:10.184" end="00:10.380">my</span> <span begin="00:10.380" end="00:10.815">decision</span> <span begin="00:10.815" end="00:10.951">on</span> <span begin="00:10.951" end="00:11.115">this</span> <span begin="00:11.115" end="00:11.402">matter</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">请记住，我对这一事项的决定</span></p><p begin="00:11.412" end="00:13.755" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:11.412" end="00:11.692">Is</span> <span begin="00:11.692" end="00:11.959">not</span> <span begin="00:11.959" end="00:12.357">subject</span> <span begin="00:12.357" end="00:12.457">to</span> <span begin="00:12.457" end="00:13.161">congressional</span> <span begin="00:13.161" end="00:13.755">approval</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">无需经过国会批准</span></p><p begin="00:13.914" end="00:16.102" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="00:13.914" end="00:14.092">The</span> <span begin="00:14.092" end="00:14.366">only</span> <span begin="00:14.366" end="00:14.616">person</span> <span begin="00:14.616" end="00:14.733">you</span> <span begin="00:14.733" end="00:14.833">have</span> <span begin="00:14.833" end="00:14.933">to</span> <span begin="00:14.933" end="00:15.573">convince</span> <span begin="00:15.714" end="00:15.859">is</span> <span begin="00:15.859" end="00:16.102">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你们唯一需要说服的人就是我</span></p><p begin="00:16.305" end="00:18.558" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="00:16.305" end="00:16.882">Secretary</span> <span begin="00:16.882" end="00:17.412">Jefferson,</span> <span begin="00:17.632" end="00:17.732">you</span> <span begin="00:17.732" end="00:17.832">have</span> <span begin="00:17.832" end="00:17.932">the</span> <span begin="00:17.932" end="00:18.262">floor,</span> <span begin="00:18.262" end="00:18.558">sir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">杰斐逊部长，请发言，先生</span></p><p begin="00:19.247" end="00:21.479" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="00:19.247" end="00:19.515">When</span> <span begin="00:19.515" end="00:19.687">we</span> <span begin="00:19.687" end="00:19.868">were</span> <span begin="00:19.868" end="00:20.056">on</span> <span begin="00:20.056" end="00:20.383">death's</span> <span begin="00:20.383" end="00:20.663">door,</span> <span begin="00:20.663" end="00:20.818">when</span> <span begin="00:20.818" end="00:20.984">we</span> <span begin="00:20.984" end="00:21.163">were</span> <span begin="00:21.163" end="00:21.479">needy</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">当我们徘徊在死亡边缘、穷困潦倒之时</span></p><p begin="00:21.719" end="00:24.015" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="00:21.719" end="00:21.926">We</span> <span begin="00:21.926" end="00:22.083">made</span> <span begin="00:22.083" end="00:22.207">a</span> <span begin="00:22.207" end="00:22.814">promise,</span> <span begin="00:22.961" end="00:23.091">we</span> <span begin="00:23.091" end="00:23.434">signed</span> <span begin="00:23.434" end="00:23.592">a</span> <span begin="00:23.592" end="00:24.015">treaty</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们许下了诺言，签署了条约</span></p><p begin="00:24.120" end="00:26.294" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="00:24.120" end="00:24.391">We</span> <span begin="00:24.391" end="00:24.581">needed</span> <span begin="00:24.581" end="00:24.888">money</span> <span begin="00:24.888" end="00:25.043">and</span> <span begin="00:25.043" end="00:25.396">guns</span> <span begin="00:25.396" end="00:25.496">and</span> <span begin="00:25.496" end="00:25.737">half</span> <span begin="00:25.737" end="00:25.864">a</span> <span begin="00:25.864" end="00:26.294">chance</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">当时我们需要钱、需要枪，哪怕只有一线生机</span></p><p begin="00:26.304" end="00:28.277" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="00:26.304" end="00:26.735">Uh,</span> <span begin="00:26.735" end="00:26.884">who</span> <span begin="00:26.884" end="00:27.378">provided</span> <span begin="00:27.378" end="00:27.664">those</span> <span begin="00:27.664" end="00:28.277">funds?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">额，是谁提供了那些资金？</span></p><p begin="00:28.400" end="00:28.766" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="00:28.400" end="00:28.766">France</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">是法国</span></p><p begin="00:29.017" end="00:31.063" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="00:29.017" end="00:29.241">In</span> <span begin="00:29.241" end="00:29.711">return,</span> <span begin="00:29.711" end="00:29.923">they</span> <span begin="00:29.923" end="00:30.303">didn't</span> <span begin="00:30.303" end="00:30.543">ask</span> <span begin="00:30.543" end="00:30.680">for</span> <span begin="00:30.680" end="00:31.063">land</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">作为回报，他们并没索要土地</span></p><p begin="00:31.294" end="00:33.283" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="00:31.294" end="00:31.723">Only</span> <span begin="00:31.723" end="00:31.823">a</span> <span begin="00:31.823" end="00:32.218">promise</span> <span begin="00:32.218" end="00:32.320">that</span> <span begin="00:32.320" end="00:32.565">we'd</span> <span begin="00:32.565" end="00:32.878">lend</span> <span begin="00:32.878" end="00:33.009">a</span> <span begin="00:33.009" end="00:33.283">hand</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">仅仅要一个我们会伸出援手的承诺</span></p><p begin="00:33.293" end="00:35.754" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="00:33.293" end="00:33.393">And</span> <span begin="00:33.393" end="00:33.721">stand</span> <span begin="00:33.721" end="00:33.882">with</span> <span begin="00:33.882" end="00:34.162">them</span> <span begin="00:34.162" end="00:34.382">if</span> <span begin="00:34.382" end="00:34.649">they</span> <span begin="00:34.649" end="00:34.959">fought</span> <span begin="00:34.959" end="00:35.274">against</span> <span begin="00:35.274" end="00:35.754">oppressors</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">承诺当他们反抗压迫者时，我们会并肩作战</span></p><p begin="00:35.764" end="00:38.110" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="00:35.764" end="00:35.898">And</span> <span begin="00:35.898" end="00:36.477">revolution</span> <span begin="00:36.477" end="00:36.611">is</span> <span begin="00:36.611" end="00:36.921">messy,</span> <span begin="00:36.921" end="00:37.082">but</span> <span begin="00:37.082" end="00:37.276">now</span> <span begin="00:37.276" end="00:37.385">is</span> <span begin="00:37.385" end="00:37.522">the</span> <span begin="00:37.522" end="00:37.707">time</span> <span begin="00:37.707" end="00:37.807">to</span> <span begin="00:37.807" end="00:38.110">stand</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">革命确实是混乱的，但现在是挺身而出的时刻了</span></p><p begin="00:38.346" end="00:40.781" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="00:38.346" end="00:38.713">Stand</span> <span begin="00:38.713" end="00:38.851">with</span> <span begin="00:38.851" end="00:38.992">our</span> <span begin="00:38.992" end="00:39.346">brothers</span> <span begin="00:39.346" end="00:39.455">as</span> <span begin="00:39.455" end="00:39.555">they</span> <span begin="00:39.555" end="00:39.897">fight</span> <span begin="00:39.897" end="00:40.202">against</span> <span begin="00:40.202" end="00:40.781">tyranny</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">与我们的兄弟们站在一起，对抗暴政</span></p><p begin="00:40.880" end="00:42.814" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="00:40.880" end="00:41.070">I</span> <span begin="00:41.070" end="00:41.322">know</span> <span begin="00:41.322" end="00:41.422">that</span> <span begin="00:41.422" end="00:42.028">Alexander</span> <span begin="00:42.028" end="00:42.486">Hamilton</span> <span begin="00:42.486" end="00:42.647">is</span> <span begin="00:42.647" end="00:42.814">here</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我知道亚历山大·汉密尔顿就在这儿</span></p><p begin="00:42.830" end="00:44.804" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L20"><span begin="00:42.830" end="00:42.961">And</span> <span begin="00:42.961" end="00:43.092">he</span> <span begin="00:43.092" end="00:43.240">would</span> <span begin="00:43.240" end="00:43.520">rather</span> <span begin="00:43.520" end="00:43.818">not</span> <span begin="00:43.818" end="00:44.133">have</span> <span begin="00:44.133" end="00:44.347">this</span> <span begin="00:44.347" end="00:44.804">debate</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">他宁愿不要进行这场辩论</span></p><p begin="00:44.904" end="00:47.905" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L21"><span begin="00:44.904" end="00:45.170">I</span> <span begin="00:45.170" end="00:45.656">remind</span> <span begin="00:45.656" end="00:45.913">you</span> <span begin="00:45.913" end="00:46.122">that</span> <span begin="00:46.122" end="00:46.290">he</span> <span begin="00:46.290" end="00:46.501">is</span> <span begin="00:46.501" end="00:46.710">not</span> <span begin="00:46.710" end="00:47.297">Secretary</span> <span begin="00:47.297" end="00:47.431">of</span> <span begin="00:47.431" end="00:47.905">State</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我得提醒你，他并不是国务卿</span></p><p begin="00:48.163" end="00:50.230" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L22"><span begin="00:48.163" end="00:48.347">He</span> <span begin="00:48.347" end="00:48.620">knows</span> <span begin="00:48.620" end="00:49.018">nothing</span> <span begin="00:49.018" end="00:49.138">of</span> <span begin="00:49.138" end="00:49.791">loyalty</span> <span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="00:49.791" end="00:50.230"><span begin="00:49.791" end="00:50.230">(Nothing)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">一窍不通</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">他对忠诚一无所知</span></p><p begin="00:50.240" end="00:52.783" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L23"><span begin="00:50.240" end="00:50.567">Smells</span> <span begin="00:50.567" end="00:50.835">like</span> <span begin="00:50.835" end="00:51.049">new</span> <span begin="00:51.049" end="00:51.394">money,</span> <span begin="00:51.394" end="00:51.775">dresses</span> <span begin="00:51.775" end="00:52.084">like</span> <span begin="00:52.084" end="00:52.352">fake</span> <span begin="00:52.352" end="00:52.783">royalty</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">闻起来像个暴发户，穿得像个假王室</span></p><p begin="00:52.785" end="00:54.525" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L24"><span begin="00:52.785" end="00:53.349">Des